sentences: Jibril Blessing (born 15 April 1988), professionally known as J Blessing or jblessing, is a Kenyan cinematographer and music video and television producer and director.
As of December 2019 he was also developing new shows for the production company, Laugh Industry.
Until 2017, Blessing was in a long-term relationship with Chantelle, with whom he had a son, who died young.
Since 2018, he has been rumored to be in a relationship with singer Avril and to have fathered a child by her, but he introduced a different woman as his girlfriend in November 2018.
